snippet.title: Judge Sides With Johnny Depp In $7 Million Suit Against Amber Heard!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Takes A Big Loss After A New York Judge Sides In Favor Of Johnny Depp In The Divorce Settlement Lawsuit!

Things are finally looking up for Johnny Depp in the current Depp and Amber Heard dispute, as the Judge sides with the Pirates of the Caribbean actor over the $7 Million Divorce Lawsuit. It appears that the court has finally chosen to favor Depp for once after years of trials and court hearings. Amber now has to show and prove if she in fact did donate the money from the divorce settlement as she promised in writing. But what triggered this change? And is Heard finally going to be held accountable for her actions?
